{"tid":447090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港遲早俾啲蝗淹沒","createTime":"2017-10-25T03:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T04:07:22.000Z","uid":93987,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a819bbda6084785828cd2dd9905912db2cb7afef","tid":447090,"uid":93987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"每日輸送啲蝗入嚟，就係想淡化香港人，令到香港人嘅比例愈嚟愈少，蝗狗嘅比例愈嚟愈多，慢慢淹沒我哋，遲啲仲食撚埋香港，有時夜晚去旺角經過個行人專用區，全撚部都係啲大陸老女人係度唱埋啲支那歌，跟住啲老蝗又要堆係度周觀阻鳩住晒，個個揸住部電話影影影，到底有乜撚嘢好影呀？有時經過母校撞正放學時間，啲師妹師弟個個講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母想點呀，搭地鐵啲大陸閪拎部電話出嚟，聽wechat啲錄音開到鬼咁死大聲，冇人想知你今晚食咩呀。香港政府根本就係同中共夾埋，慢慢噉吞撚咗我哋個香港，巴絲們想唔想像到第時落街，啲人十個有九個大陸狗嘅畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5fa50cf175193db40aff35a8bffb0727e415c3","tid":447090,"uid":93987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:14:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，第時行行下街踩到屎，以為係狗屎啦，其實係啲支那狗周街開餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2679e9dbaade409f26dd9f556d1e07b5d2d397","tid":447090,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"咁你打算生仔抗共定逆洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6beaf001602b059d124e2a33b0d67030ce03d8","tid":447090,"uid":93987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你打算生仔抗共定逆洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撚用咩，依家連啲學校都洗埋啲學生嘅腦，生個仔隨時反自己"},{"pid":"79d9bc442894535b3c502c0cc56dc733add2054e","tid":447090,"uid":6648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"已經淹沒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cc328cf94d694bf702965f2c77f1ae2b69abed","tid":447090,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁你打算生仔抗共定逆洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撚用咩，依家連啲學校都洗埋啲學生嘅腦，生個仔隨時反自己</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失敗主義撚"},{"pid":"56db351b75bda4feff03fd4a86110beba8660451","tid":447090,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"每日150 個  過多十年廿年邊頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17818dad401d51bfb67881ff7a54b1debb38aeb9","tid":447090,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"遲早?"},{"pid":"5c2efc6732b139087bca7e753677ee993ceaf79b","tid":447090,"uid":93987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日150 個  過多十年廿年邊頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每年54000幾個蝗過嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9db8d1a5acfedde476f974cf9620fc9ad5f815","tid":447090,"uid":50995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"喺地鐵用電話開喇叭播啲蝗語劇 成個車廂一齊受"},{"pid":"90ce9b7986a4a35351a029ba1785772788e2e6d8","tid":447090,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:03:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"618a14f367e7ec76ae30ac116e8a497bd52116df","tid":447090,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"一年有數以萬計既蝗，不過傳媒同五毛只會集中講蝻"}]}